	ing courses\, hands-on workshops\, free events\, and professional certific
	ate programs. Have your work reviewed\, and receive a free personal consul
	tation from Natan Dvir and a 10% discount on Summer classes.RSVP is requir
	ed via this link.\n\nhttps://www.edu.hcponline.org/events/summer26-open-ho
	use\n\nFrom Houston Center for Photography
